{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142890/extras/lava_run.gif?t=1728418705\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142890/extras/separator_helmet_2x.png?t=1728418705\" /><br><br>Trophy Knight is a Metroid style action platformer. Part treasure hunt, part noble adventure story, our hero is on a journey to find and defeat the ultimate foe. Guided by some mysterious voices, he will travel far and wide on a quest for redemption.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142890/extras/hank_boss.gif?t=1728418705\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142890/extras/separator_helmet_2x.png?t=1728418705\" /><br>After each successful boss fight, the player gets to pick up a trophy and bring it back to the trophy room for all to admire. But it is not always easy to navigate those narrow dungeon corridors when your hands are full. Definitely watch your head and mind the gap.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142890/extras/goo_drop.gif?t=1728418705\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142890/extras/separator_helmet_2x.png?t=1728418705\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Classic pixel art side scrolling action and adventure.<br></li><li>Exquisite environments with smooth parallax and lighting effects.<br></li><li>Explore ancient ruins, desolate lands and deep dungeons.<br></li><li>Fight epic bosses and put them on display in your trophy room.<br></li><li>Collect and upgrade new weapons.<br></li><li>Level up to fight even epic-er bosses!</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142890/